<title>USA: ADR REPORT - Chinese companies rally.</title>
<headline>ADR REPORT - Chinese companies rally.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Chinese companies were some of the biggest percentage gainers on the New York Stock Exchange on Wednesday as a rally in their stocks in Hong Kong extended to their American Depositary Receipts (ADRs) in the United States, traders said.</p>
<p>One dealer said their ADRs were reacting to news that many of these companies were planning to restructure.</p>
<p>Four Chinese companies were among the exchange's top 10 percentage gainers in early trade.</p>
